---
title: Spiced Winter Stew with Roasted Root Veggies and Bulgur Wheat
description: There is so much going on in this delicious vegetarian dish - earthy herb roasted root veggies, a rich tomatoey stew, nutty bulgur wheat and a minty yoghurt sauce, making every mouthful of this dish a total delight. Packed  with good-for-you ingredients, this warming stew is the perfect alternative to a curry and a delicious way to fill up on your veg.
